cgcloud__RBF_Product_Manual_Input__c.name: cgcloud__RBF_Product_Manual_Input__c
cgcloud__RBF_Product_Manual_Input__c.description: This object represents the junction between Rate-based Funding and Product.

cgcloud__Edit_Time__c.description: Sequences a user's manual edits to the grid data.

cgcloud__External_Id__c.description: Federated ID - concatenating Rate-based_Funding__c and Product2.

cgcloud__Measure_Code__c.description: Measure Code of the manual calculation input entry that this record defines.

cgcloud__Product__c.description: Product to which the manual calculation input entry that's defined by this record is anchored. If the entry is at the total level, the value of this field can be null.

cgcloud__Rate_based_Funding__c.description: Rate based funding to which the manual calculation input entry belongs.

cgcloud__Value__c.description: User-provided value of the manual calculation input entry.
